ODE IV

TO XANTHIAS

OURT a handmaid, Xanthias Phoceus?

'T is no shame at all.

Slave Briseis tamed Achilles, Proud before his fall.

Kingly Telamonian Ajax Slave Tecmessa moved ; And Atrides, in mid triumph,

Captive virgin loved;
